    "description": "Explore the forgotten and abandoned summer camp &quot;Camp Funtime&quot;. Explore and solve puzzles all while looking for clues as to why the camp was shut down, but be careful because there are horrors waiting to happen at every turn.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to Camp Funtime</strong></h2>Camp Funtime was once the best summer camp to go to. That was until it was permanently shut down from the public. No one got a proper explanation as to why the camp was shut down but that's where you come in. Try to survive and uncover the mysteries of the facility.... and don't get caught.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/3b588af07da4e3e9721bde1c14d9a1e8.poster.avif?t=1739323281\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/3b588af07da4e3e9721bde1c14d9a1e8.webm?t=1739323281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/3b588af07da4e3e9721bde1c14d9a1e8.mp4?t=1739323281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meet Captain Kitty</strong></h2>Captain Kitty is a custom made animatronic made with one purpose, to spread laughter and joy to everyone he comes into contact with. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/0f10fb7435ceb681ffed4187d98594a9.poster.avif?t=1739323281\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/0f10fb7435ceb681ffed4187d98594a9.webm?t=1739323281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/0f10fb7435ceb681ffed4187d98594a9.mp4?t=1739323281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exploring the camp</strong></h2>The camp is split into different areas that can all be reached by using our train system!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/f171d34062681a38409142b3678e48f2.poster.avif?t=1739323281\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/f171d34062681a38409142b3678e48f2.webm?t=1739323281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/f171d34062681a38409142b3678e48f2.mp4?t=1739323281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>School Sector</li></ul>While your kids are here, they will be taking educational and fun classes throughout their day. The school sector is home to our classrooms, cafeteria, and the gymnasium!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/e86f2a12fa6b48ba3665df6af630bda4.poster.avif?t=1739323281\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/e86f2a12fa6b48ba3665df6af630bda4.webm?t=1739323281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/e86f2a12fa6b48ba3665df6af630bda4.mp4?t=1739323281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Playground Sector</li></ul>Once your kids are done for the day, they have free time inside our custom-built playground located at the center of the camp! This giant playground was made with one intent... To ensure your kids have a &quot;Funtime&quot; while they are here. Play hide and seek, tag, or explore the playpark. Whatever your kids desire to play we have it all at our playground!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039870/extras/fecfb794bafdb216144d970829723b21.avif?t=1739323281\" width=608 height=174 /></span><br><br>Will your kids be joining us? There's lots of fun to be had at &quot;Camp Funtime&quot;...",
